comment: * Helper class for creating a {@link SipProfile}.

methods.name: public Builder setAuthUserName(String name)
methods.comment:
* Sets the username used for authentication.
         *
         * @param name authentication username of the profile
         * @return this builder object

methods.name: public Builder setProfileName(String name)
methods.comment:
* Sets the name of the profile. This name is given by user.
         *
         * @param name name of the profile
         * @return this builder object

methods.name: public Builder setPassword(String password)
methods.comment:
* Sets the password of the SIP account
         *
         * @param password password of the SIP account
         * @return this builder object

methods.name: public Builder setPort(int port) throws IllegalArgumentException
methods.comment:
* Sets the port number of the server. By default, it is 5060.
         *
         * @param port port number of the server
         * @return this builder object
         * @throws IllegalArgumentException if the port number is out of range

methods.name: public Builder setProtocol(String protocol) throws IllegalArgumentException
methods.comment:
* Sets the protocol used to connect to the SIP server. Currently,
         * only "UDP" and "TCP" are supported.
         *
         * @param protocol the protocol string
         * @return this builder object
         * @throws IllegalArgumentException if the protocol is not recognized

methods.name: public Builder setOutboundProxy(String outboundProxy)
methods.comment:
* Sets the outbound proxy of the SIP server.
         *
         * @param outboundProxy the network address of the outbound proxy
         * @return this builder object

methods.name: public Builder setDisplayName(String displayName)
methods.comment:
* Sets the display name of the user.
         *
         * @param displayName display name of the user
         * @return this builder object

methods.name: public Builder setSendKeepAlive(boolean flag)
methods.comment:
* Sets the send keep-alive flag.
         *
         * @param flag true if sending keep-alive message is required,
         *      false otherwise
         * @return this builder object

methods.name: public Builder setAutoRegistration(boolean flag)
methods.comment:
* Sets the auto. registration flag.
         *
         * @param flag true if the profile will be registered automatically,
         *      false otherwise
         * @return this builder object

methods.name: public SipProfile build()
methods.comment:
* Builds and returns the SIP profile object.
         *
         * @return the profile object created

public Builder setProtocol(String protocol) throws IllegalArgumentException
